SGX is also a listed, for-proﬁt entity with a widely distributed ownership and shareholder base. This gives rise to Self—Regulatory obligations. We employ the highest standards in carrying out our dual role and ensure that any potential conﬂicts between our responsibilities as a regulator and as a listed company are adequately addressed.
